Package com.flipkart.bean

Class FlipFitCenter

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitCenter
public class FlipFitCenter extends Object
FlipFitCenter class represents a fitness center entity in the FlipFit system. It encapsulates information about a fitness center, including its unique identifier, owner details, name, GST identification number, location, capacity, price, and approval status.
